36:51.460 --> 36:52.245
Hey.

36:53.330 --> 36:56.572
Oh... Oh, damn.

36:56.580 --> 36:59.378
Hey. Bad dream?

36:59.380 --> 37:01.325
Yeah.

37:01.330 --> 37:03.207
You _can tell me
about It, you know?

37:04.330 --> 37:06.070
Huh.No.

37:06.080 --> 37:09.379
Have you having nightmares
about my dad, too? Yeah, no.

37:09.380 --> 37:10.449
No, thanks.

37:10.460 --> 37:11.779
Why don't you tell me more

37:11.790 --> 37:13.530
about what happened
that night?

37:13.540 --> 37:15.417
Maybe it'll help.

37:15.420 --> 37:18.241
You do not want inside my head
with all that, trust me.

37:18.250 --> 37:21.458
Yeah, well,
I don't want you to be
in there alone, either.

37:25.170 --> 37:27.240
I know
that it was an accident.

37:27.250 --> 37:29.491
Did you see it happen?

37:29.500 --> 37:30.660
[sniffs]

37:30.670 --> 37:32.410
I was ten feet
away from hIm.

37:33.460 --> 37:35.746
You saw him go over?

37:37.290 --> 37:38.325
Yeah.

37:41.540 --> 37:42.666
Yeah, I saw him.

37:47.670 --> 37:49.911
He didn't stand a chance.

37:51.540 --> 37:52.746
And me, I just...

37:54.750 --> 37:56.320
I didn't do anything
to stop it.

37:59.790 --> 38:02.372
It wasn't
your fault, Xander.

38:02.380 --> 38:05.497
It was an accident.

38:05.500 --> 38:07.821
Accidents happen.

38:07.830 --> 38:08.990
Please, just-just-just...

38:09.000 --> 38:11.412
just stop saying
that word, okay?

38:11.420 --> 38:12.489
What?

38:12.500 --> 38:14.206
Okay.

38:14.210 --> 38:16.030
It wasn't a damn accident.

38:20.620 --> 38:22.417
Dad was murdered.

38:29.960 --> 38:31.075
By who?

38:35.500 --> 38:37.036
I didn't see his face.

38:39.580 --> 38:41.161
[sniffs]

38:41.170 --> 38:44.458
There were other boats
on the water that night.

38:44.460 --> 38:47.418
The guy must have came
from one of them.

38:59.250 --> 39:00.990
Everything okay?

39:01.000 --> 39:03.457
The readings aren't
like anything I've ever seen.

39:03.460 --> 39:04.666
Did you hear anything?

39:04.670 --> 39:07.457
No, but we got it.

39:12.040 --> 39:13.371
Everything okay?

39:14.620 --> 39:15.609
Yes.

39:15.620 --> 39:18.282
Maddie say my song is

39:20.540 --> 39:21.746
recorded.

39:21.750 --> 39:24.708
No need sing anymore.

39:27.540 --> 39:29.496
I go back to others.

39:29.500 --> 39:30.740
Sleep.

39:46.670 --> 39:47.659
[beep]

39:47.670 --> 39:50.070
[line ringing]

39:50.080 --> 39:51.456
Hey, it's Ben.
Leave a message.

39:51.460 --> 39:54.111
-[beeps]
-It's Helen.

39:54.120 --> 39:58.113
I don't know what changed
your mom's mind,

39:58.120 --> 40:00.168
but I am staring at a check,

40:02.710 --> 40:04.280
and I found Rick Marzdan.

40:05.620 --> 40:08.498
Now I have to figure out
how to tell him.

40:16.880 --> 40:19.326
[groaning]

40:30.500 --> 40:33.207
[gasping]

40:44.170 --> 40:47.822
[female singer]
There's a storm

40:47.830 --> 40:49.786
Thunder and lightning

40:49.790 --> 40:54.033
Dear, in your

40:54.040 --> 40:55.746
Eyes it's frightening

40:55.750 --> 40:57.570
-[pounding]
-Damn it!

41:05.750 --> 41:10.289
All my life

41:10.290 --> 41:11.780
I'm trying to get it right

41:11.790 --> 41:15.612
You came in

41:15.620 --> 41:17.531
And you took me by surprise

41:17.540 --> 41:21.613
Now I'm drowning

41:21.620 --> 41:23.702
Under the weight of your

41:23.710 --> 41:27.703
Pre-cious crimes

41:27.710 --> 41:30.531
My body's sinking

41:30.540 --> 41:32.747
[placid high-pitched call]

41:37.790 --> 41:40.497
[music playing]
